{"tid":2204650,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】有冇高質黃店居酒屋好食？","createTime":"2020-09-16T08:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T09:54:01.000Z","uid":345352,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8473e231c19bcb9ef2902a222ea946004aebe94f","tid":2204650,"uid":345352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:16:44.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">絕對唔會係申子居酒屋先囉！！！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔住各位有少少假標題。<br />\n香港人對日餐嘅需求十分大，亦相信連登嘅各位平時會揀有良心黃店食。<br />\n有見及此，樓主接受另一同事請求，揭穿申子居酒屋黑心嘅真面目。<br />\n同時希望大家集思廣益放一啲好食高質嘅居酒屋出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n係正文開始前，樓主希望幫一個抗爭IG作宣傳，入面第三集有一啲關於黃色經濟圈嘅話題值得一聽。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hongkong_valiantspeaks/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhongkong_valiantspeaks%2F&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=c04cbf2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hongkong_valiantspeaks/</a><br />\n當前更重要嘅亦係十二手足安危，聯署雖然達標但唔足夠表達港人心切。<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-release-12-hong-kong-protesters-under-chinese-custody\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-demand-release-12-hong-kong-protesters-under-chinese-custody&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=fbd09da8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-release-12-hong-kong-protesters-under-chinese-custody</a><br />\n香港人必須強身健體，修文習武。<br />\n正文:<br />\n話說如果你琴日有嚟申子居酒屋食飯，應該知道個老細俾個員工當面屌完劈炮。<br />\n就係嗰位同事拜託我揭發呢間店，但係礙於保密協議，呢位同事發言内容稍有局限，樓主會集一眾前/現任員工心聲放出嚟等大家自行判斷仲應唔應該幫襯呢間店。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">同事A:</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pnLKJyB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpnLKJyB.png&h=48799ac0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0wdMcrW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0wdMcrW.png&h=c99c2fce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">同事B:</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/10kZxwF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F10kZxwF.png&h=44fc1997&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sXf6WYk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsXf6WYk.png&h=e2ac5002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUxQEbW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUxQEbW.png&h=aa002ab9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">同事C:</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2fEb75d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2fEb75d.png&h=d6dd64d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1geoeLd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1geoeLd.png&h=456e2d82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">同事D:</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ztkCjb0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FztkCjb0.png&h=4dc11a04&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R1YcSw0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR1YcSw0.png&h=1f61d7d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上流傳:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tz4C3DK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftz4C3DK.png&h=77835d24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到呢到都冇乜好講，如果到呢一刻都選擇去食呢間店，我會覺得你只係想借食黃店贖罪。"},{"pid":"1a36bf20b1e46c2aa54e30c2b46e9a7a50fdb8c9","tid":2204650,"uid":255976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:17:51.000Z","msg":"HOKAHOKA"},{"pid":"29ebb3cd16e4abc6f622d1edae236760860c4461","tid":2204650,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"老花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇精華"},{"pid":"bfb3ffb9229558fed48abfe32b010fb718866024","tid":2204650,"uid":28004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:58:33.000Z","msg":"八寸"},{"pid":"bd1082aa28fb1ae95c52277693575a637bb1b817","tid":2204650,"uid":12492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:03:12.000Z","msg":"風流居酒屋"},{"pid":"65b1ed2f4ff2660df6e0f0e931816f650612aa1a","tid":2204650,"uid":345352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29ebb3cd16e4abc6f622d1edae236760860c4461","tid":2204650,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"老花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇精華"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:54:01.000Z","msg":"簡單嚟講，除咗個人聲稱黄之外，做嘅嘢全部都係仆街嘢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}